In the District Court of the territory of Washington in and for the fourth Judicial District therof, holding terms at Spokane Falls, Spokane County, in said territory.
To the sheriff of Spokane County, Greetings
In the name of the UNited States, Yuu are hereby commanded to Summon JJ.M C Faling J.M. Grant

to be and appear before the District Court, at the Court House, in Spokane Falls in said County, on the 9th day of July A.D. 1887 at ten O'Clock A.M., to here give evidence in the above entitled case on part of said defendant there to remain discharfed
